2003-06-24 09:33  Peter Naulls  <peter@chocky.org>

	* m_cpumem.c, regression, regression/loadstore.s, targetcpu.c,
	targetcpu.h: Fix behaviour of ldr/str h/sb
	Add some token XScale support
